OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,FSome parents are having to choose
OL,7,Fbetween feeding their children and
OL,8,Fbuying school clothes, according to
OL,9,FChannel Island charities.
OL,11,FThe Shiloh Church in Guernsey's second-
OL,12,Fhand uniform bank says it has been
OL,13,Foverwhelmed with families seeking
OL,14,Faffordable items for their children.
OL,16,FChrissy Salmon, team leader at church,
OL,17,Fexplains: "When there's a change in
OL,18,Fseason and your child changes so much
OL,19,Fover the course of the year, it's
OL,20,Freally expensive for families.
