OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,F"People and families are struggling
OL,7,Fmore than ever with the cost of
OL,8,Fliving."
OL,10,FFor many working parents balancing
OL,11,Ffull-time jobs while looking after
OL,12,Fchildren in the summer holidays, the
OL,13,Fstart of the new school year may come
OL,14,Fas a relief - but it also comes at a
OL,15,Fcost.
OL,17,FIt is a similar issue in Jersey, where
OL,18,Fthe average school uniform will set
OL,19,Fparents back #114 annually.
