OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,FIn 2023, the island's government
OL,7,Fintroduced a policy to limit the
OL,8,Fnumber of bespoke school uniform items
OL,9,Fto five per student.
OL,11,FHowever, schools are not required to
OL,12,Ffully comply with these rules until
OL,13,FSeptember 2026 and they do not apply
OL,14,Fto private and fee-paying schools.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, in the UK, the British
OL,17,FGovernment plans to limit the number
OL,18,Fof compulsory branded items to three,
OL,19,Fexcluding ties.
