OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,FYet for some, this is not enough to
OL,7,Fease the financial burden that the new
OL,8,Fschool year brings.
OL,10,FOne parent tells ITV News they have
OL,11,Fhad to resort to sourcing more
OL,12,Faffordable uniform options online,
OL,13,Fwhich has led to them buying items
OL,14,Fthat are either the wrong colour or
OL,15,Fsize.
OL,17,FThe problem is said to have been
OL,18,Fexacerbated by the closure of school
OL,19,Funiform vendors, including the JSSK
OL,20,FJersey Schools and Sports Kit store at
OL,21,FLes Quennevais.
