OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,FThe store closed last year, citing
OL,7,Ffinancial difficulties in meeting the
OL,8,Fnew policy limits announced by the
OL,9,FGovernment.
OL,11,FVariety, the Children's Charity of
OL,12,FJersey, provides vouchers to families
OL,13,Fstruggling to fund school uniform
OL,14,Fitems, but says that some major
OL,15,Fretailers do not accept the vouchers
OL,16,Flocally.
OL,18,FSandra Auckland from the charity adds:
OL,19,F"It's causing a lot of problems as we
OL,20,Fcan only go to the more expensive
OL,21,Fstores.
