OL,3,CFamilies 'choosing between feeding
OL,4,Cchildren and buying school uniform'
OL,6,F"It's important that when children
OL,7,Fstart school they all look the same,
OL,8,Fbut it's just becoming so expensive
OL,9,Ffor families to buy all the uniform
OL,10,Fitems their child needs."
OL,12,FThe States of Guernsey offers grants
OL,13,Ffor parents and Jersey's Education
OL,14,FMinister, Deputy Rob Ward, says: "Many
OL,15,Fschools have already taken positive
OL,16,Fsteps to simplify their uniform
OL,17,Frequirements, reduce the number of
OL,18,Fbranded items and provide affordable
OL,19,Foptions that allow parents to purchase
OL,20,Fclothing from a variety of local
OL,21,Fretailers.
