OL,6,FHe does, however, understand it can be
OL,7,Fa challenging time for families to get
OL,8,Fwhat they need for the new term and
OL,9,Fadds: "Families who have concerns or
OL,10,Fneed additional help are encouraged to
OL,11,Fspeak directly with their school,
OL,12,Fwhere staff are ready to provide
OL,13,Fsupport in a confidential and
OL,14,Frespectful manner."
